        crm:P3_has_note          "Live, read-only web map displaying two operational layers: current meteorological warning coverage and enriched CH sites. Hosted on ArcGIS Online as Feature Layers or consumed from standards-based endpoints, configured to re-query the service automatically at fixed intervals coordinated with the refresh rate of meteorological warnings. Uses awareness levels (1–3) and site risk classes (a–c) to colour, label and filter content. Demonstrator layer consuming middleware outputs; not core infrastructure." ;
        aocat:has_functionality  <urn:uuid:aca4b2c8-dd20-4802-9d8f-6a9823aeecd1> , <urn:uuid:e97e5d48-d18f-4a7d-a5a2-fb2b52d471c9> , <urn:uuid:dc0653be-3a72-4a2f-93cf-b9f8cdd1d9ae> , <urn:uuid:bc8931de-2ff5-4f87-b9e3-6655969391b3> .

